source:
TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
The sentry captain fears for the fate of one of his men.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>Règle spéciale<var 1D /var>:  synchronisation de quête<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
Il semblerait qu'un soldat manque à l'appel de la garnison de L'Impératif d'Ostall.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_TODO_01<tab>Search for the amaro once again.
TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_TODO_02<tab>Use the healing salve on the wounded sentry.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_TODO_02<tab>Utiliser le <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8F900202 /var> sur le soldat blessé

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_TODO_03<tab>Report back to the sentry captain.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_TODO_03<tab>Faire votre rapport au capitaine de la garnison

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_000<tab>Damn it all! We can ill afford to lose another─ Ho there, friend. Might you lend me your aid? One of my best men has yet to return from his patrol, and I fear the worst.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_000<tab>Voyage<var 08 E905 ((use)) ((ur)) /var><var 1D /var>! Désolé de t'importuner, mais j'ai vraiment besoin d'aide<var 1D /var>! Un de mes soldats n'est pas revenu de sa patrouille, son amaro est rentré tout seul<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_001<tab>As you can see, his amaro made it back safely, but my man's nowhere to be found. Could you search for him in my stead? I would go myself, but I can't very well abandon my post.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_001<tab>Tout le monde est à sa recherche, mais on ne l'a toujours pas trouvé<var 1D /var>! Tu pourrais nous aider<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_003<tab>Bloody beast! Where do you think you're─ Ah, too late I suppose. But wait... Do you reckon he's gone back for his rider?
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_003<tab>A-attends<var 1D /var>!! Reviens<var 1D /var>!!! Où est-ce qu'il va<var 1D /var>? Tu crois qu'il veut nous indiquer l'endroit où est son cavalier<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_004<tab>Sorry to trouble you, friend, but do you think you could follow that amaro for us? That scaly brute might be my best chance at finding our man.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_004<tab>Désolé de te demander ça, mais tu peux t'occuper de le suivre<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_005<tab>And take this salve with you. I reckon there's a good chance he's out there, too wounded to have made his way back.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_005<tab>Il est possible que mon soldat soit blessé et ne puisse pas bouger quand tu le trouveras. Prends ce <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8F900202 /var> au cas où<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_010<tab>Pray follow that amaro, friend! That beast might be our best hope to track down my missing man.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_010<tab>Suis cet amaro, peut-être qu'il t'amènera au soldat<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SYSTEM_000_020<tab>The amaro stares intently in the general direction of Dampsole.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SYSTEM_000_020<tab>L'amaro regarde dans la direction de Foulebourbe en gémissant...

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_030<tab>Gah! Damned fiend got me in the leg... I can barely stand, let alone move. Is this the end for me?
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_030<tab>Hah, je... J'ai été attaqué... Je suis blessé...

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SYSTEM_000_040<tab>The amaro eyes the wounded soldier with a gaze that could almost be described as concerned. This must be the sentry who was separated from his mount.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SYSTEM_000_040<tab>L'amaro regarde le soldat au sol et semble inquiet... C'est cer<var 16 /var>tai<var 16 /var>ne<var 16 /var>ment son cavalier.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SYSTEM_000_042<tab>The amaro eyes you with an expectant gaze. You sense it is hoping that you will tend to the man's wounds.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SYSTEM_000_042<tab>L'amaro semble essayer de vous dire quelque chose. Utilisez le <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8F900202 /var> sur le soldat au sol.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SYSTEM_000_051<tab>The amaro eyes you with an expectant gaze. You sense it is hoping that you will tend to the man's wounds.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SYSTEM_000_051<tab>L'amaro semble essayer de vous dire quelque chose. Utilisez le <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8F900202 /var> sur le soldat au sol.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_060<tab>Thank you, friend! When the beast knocked me from my mount, I thought it was the end of me for sure! But however did you know where to look?
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_060<tab>Ouf... Merci... Grâce à vous, je me sens beaucoup mieux<var 1D /var>! Mais, comment m'avez-vous trouvé<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_061<tab>My mount led you to me? You don't say!
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_061<tab>Je vois, tout le monde était inquiet pour moi...

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_062<tab>I owe you an apology, little fellow... Here I thought you ran off in fear of my foe, but it turns out you were looking for help the whole time. Can you forgive me for doubting you?
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_062<tab>Et moi qui pensais que mon amaro s'était enfui en me laissant ici, alors qu'il était parti chercher de l'aide<var 1D /var>! C'est vraiment un compagnon fidèle<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_064<tab>And with that, I'd best head back to the Imperative and let everyone know I'm all right. Thank you, my friend. You saved my life today.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTPRIVATE03385_000_064<tab>Je file prévenir mon supérieur de ce pas<var 1D /var>! Merci d'être venu<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> me sauver, voyage<var 08 E905 ((use)) ((ur)) /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_070<tab>Ah, there you are. I was hoping that you'd return so I could properly express my gratitude. You'll be happy to know─as I would─that my man has safely returned to the Imperative.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_070<tab>Ah, te revoilà<var 1D /var>! J'ai appris ce qu'il s'était passé, merci d'être venu<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> en aide à mon soldat<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_071<tab>Those amaro can be stubborn brutes at times, but times like this make a man appreciate what loyal companions they truly are. I'd say this one's earned himself some extra feed for dinner today!
target: TEXT_LUCKZC002_03385_SCOUTCHIEF03385_000_071<tab>Je n'aurais jamais pensé que son amaro vienne nous prévenir pour qu'on aille le sauver<var 1D /var>! Il mérite bien une petite friandise ou deux<var 1D /var>! J'y vais de ce pas<var 1D /var>! À bientôt, voyage<var 08 E905 ((use)) ((ur)) /var>, et merci encore<var 1D /var>!
